strings: <voice_0x01001916><se_low>Boiler: Now we know what happened. A sad ending for Lagos.
<voice_0x01001917><se_low>King of tricks: If you knew what an evil clown, you wouldn't let him cross that threshold!
<voice_0x01001919><se_low>King of tricks: Although I have to say that Lira is a clumsy teacher.
<voice_0x0100191A><se_low>King of tricks: You need to understand the server's requirements and state of mind. No wonder it doesn't have a "hard" finish.
<voice_0x0100191B><se_low>Boiler: There is nothing left of the crystal ball today. Beautiful evening
<voice_0x0100191C><se_low>Boiler: Next time you visit this huge cauldron, try again. it's probably not free
